{"body": "Change `self.delegate = self.new` to `self.delegate ||= self.new` to prevent against the case where self.delegate has been set by the subclass of Migration.\r\n\r\nAlso, removed the superclass.delegate check since delegate won't ever be nil.  I don't believe there's a valid case where delegate should ever be nil, as calling any of the migration commands on ActiveRecord::Migration doesn't do anything. ", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/1715098", "created_at": "2011-08-03T02:40:02Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/2357#issuecomment-1715098", "updated_at": "2011-08-03T02:40:02Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 2357, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/cmeiklejohn/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/cmeiklejohn/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/cmeiklejohn/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/cmeiklejohn", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/cmeiklejohn/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/cmeiklejohn", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/cmeiklejohn/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/3e09fee7b359be847ed5fa48f524a3d3?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F7cbabebc4ff57faf9cd22b4188243793.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/cmeiklejohn/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/cmeiklejohn/received_events", "gravatar_id": "3e09fee7b359be847ed5fa48f524a3d3", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/cmeiklejohn/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "cmeiklejohn", "type": "User", "id": 44939, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/cmeiklejohn/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "52384453bd3543c151010cfe"}, "id": 1715098, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/2357"}
